{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-about-js","path":"/about/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"education최신순\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#education%EC%B5%9C%EC%8B%A0%EC%88%9C\" aria-label=\"education최신순 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>EDUCATION(최신순)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>[프론트엔드 스쿨 과정 수료] - 패스트캠퍼스, 서울. 2017.01 - 04</li>\n<li>[Intro to Programming Nano Degree 수료] - Udacity. 2016.</li>\n<li>[경영학부 경영학 전공, 3.21/4.5] - 성균관대학교, 서울. 2005 - 2014.</li>\n<li>[미술대학 예술학 전공, 2.73/4.5] - 홍익대학교, 서울. 2006 - 2010(2학년 중퇴, 군 복무 기간 포함)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"work-experiences최신순\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#work-experiences%EC%B5%9C%EC%8B%A0%EC%88%9C\" aria-label=\"work experiences최신순 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>WORK EXPERIENCES(최신순)</h2>\n<h3 id=\"프리랜서-202005---현재\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%84%EB%A6%AC%EB%9E%9C%EC%84%9C-202005---%ED%98%84%EC%9E%AC\" aria-label=\"프리랜서 202005   현재 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>프리랜서. 2020.05 - 현재</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>중앙대학교 실내환경디자인학과 졸업전시회 <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://20chicgrad.netlify.app/\">웹 애플리케이션 개발</a>. 2020.10 - 2020.11</p>\n<ul>\n<li>ReactJS, styled-components, Google Firestore, GatsbyJS, Netlify</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>React Native 활용 애플리케이션 프론트엔드 개발 참여(뚝딱). 2020.07 - 2020.09</p>\n<ul>\n<li>React Native, MobX</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"인프랩--프론트엔드-개발자-201810---202004\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B8%ED%94%84%EB%9E%A9--%ED%94%84%EB%A1%A0%ED%8A%B8%EC%97%94%EB%93%9C-%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EC%9E%90-201810---202004\" aria-label=\"인프랩  프론트엔드 개발자 201810   202004 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>인프랩 / 프론트엔드 개발자. 2018.10 - 2020.04</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>온라인 강의 수강 플랫폼 <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.inflearn.com/\">인프런</a> 웹 애플리케이션 개발.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>VanillaJS(ES6+), NodeJS(ExpressJS), Webpack, Scss, FxJS, FxDomJS</li>\n<li>함수형 패러다임을 적용한 VanillaJS 기반의 작업.</li>\n<li>Linting, Testing 자동화, 코드 리뷰 과정, Sprint 및 데일리 스탠드업 미팅 도입으로 개발 프로세스 개선에 기여.\t</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<ul>\n<li>NextJS, ReactJS, styled-components 활용한 인프런 어드민 페이지 개발.</li>\n<li>WebView 기반의 React Native Android Application 개발.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"zeppelinx--프론트엔드-개발자-201808---201810\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#zeppelinx--%ED%94%84%EB%A1%A0%ED%8A%B8%EC%97%94%EB%93%9C-%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EC%9E%90-201808---201810\" aria-label=\"zeppelinx  프론트엔드 개발자 201808   201810 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ZeppelinX / 프론트엔드 개발자. 2018.08 - 2018.10</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>데이터 분석 플랫폼 <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://zepl.com/\">zepl.com</a> 개발 및 유지 보수. Angular 기반의 웹 서비스를 React로 마이그레이션.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>ReactJS, Redux, Jest, Enzyme, Sass, Webpack, Babel, ES6+</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"텀블벅--프론트엔드-개발자-201707---201804\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%85%80%EB%B8%94%EB%B2%85--%ED%94%84%EB%A1%A0%ED%8A%B8%EC%97%94%EB%93%9C-%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EC%9E%90-201707---201804\" aria-label=\"텀블벅  프론트엔드 개발자 201707   201804 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>텀블벅 / 프론트엔드 개발자. 2017.07 - 2018.04</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>크라우드 펀딩 플랫폼 <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://tumblbug.com/\">텀블벅</a> 웹 애플리케이션 개발 및 유지 보수</p>\n<ul>\n<li>ReactJS, MobX, Styled-components, Flow, Jest, Enzyme, Webpack, Babel, RoR 기반 SSR을 SPA로 마이그레이션</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>새로운 웹 서비스 개발(미공개)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>ReactJS, Typescript, NextJS, GraphQL, React-Apollo</li>\n<li>재사용 가능한 UI  React Component를 구성하고 제품에 적용하는 작업을 주로 진행</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"한화-lc--회계팀-사원-201406---201606\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%9C%ED%99%94-lc--%ED%9A%8C%EA%B3%84%ED%8C%80-%EC%82%AC%EC%9B%90-201406---201606\" aria-label=\"한화 lc  회계팀 사원 201406   201606 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>한화 L&#x26;C / 회계팀 사원. 2014.06 - 2016.06</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Oracle ERP AP, AR, 급여 관련 세무 업무, 4대 보험, 부가세</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"대한민국-공군-200707---200909\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8C%80%ED%95%9C%EB%AF%BC%EA%B5%AD-%EA%B3%B5%EA%B5%B0-200707---200909\" aria-label=\"대한민국 공군 200707   200909 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 